message.content: "cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CL". The paper deals with a task of embodied question answering, which involves navigation, perception, and reasoning. This task is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), and natural language processing (cs.CL). Given that the paper proposes a new architecture for the task and presents experimental results, it is likely to be submitted to one of these sub-categories.
